sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant FE as Search.jsx (React)
    participant RT as search router (api/routes/search.py)
    participant EMB as etl.transform
    participant DB as PostgreSQL + pgvector
    participant LLM as Groq LLM (etl.llm.complete)

    U->>FE: type query q
    FE->>RT: GET /search?q=...
    RT->>EMB: embeddings_available()

    alt embedding model cached
        EMB-->>RT: true
        RT->>EMB: get_embedding(q)
        EMB-->>RT: query vector
        RT->>DB: ORDER BY embedding <=> vector LIMIT n
        DB-->>RT: ranked rows + similarity
    else model not cached (fallback)
        EMB-->>RT: false
        RT->>DB: full-text tsvector / websearch_to_tsquery match
        DB-->>RT: text-match candidates
        RT->>DB: recent articles (fill candidate pool)
        DB-->>RT: recent rows
        RT->>LLM: rank candidates by relevance (_ai_rank)
        LLM-->>RT: ordered article ids (JSON)
    end

    RT-->>FE: id, title, source, sentiment, topic_label, similarity
    FE-->>U: render result cards
